1.6.0
-----

* Fix getLogger when called twice and passing different extras
* Replace Travis by CircleCI
* Add documentation for the ExtrasFormatter class
* Move to Mergify v2

1.5.0
-----

* formatter: enable extra keywords by default

1.4.0
